name: Warehouse of the Ted
description:
You are Ted. You work at a warehouse. You need to deliver as many packages as possible, despite being weighed down by a ball-and-chain. No worries, you are TED. Ted can throw his way around the warehouse!

Controls:

Keyboard: 

Move - WASD 

Action - K

Skip - 3

Numpad:

Move - 8456

Action - 7

Skip - 3

Created using: Godot 4
Created for Nokia Jam 5 https://itch.io/jam/nokiajam5
